# Source code and our own annotations (net connectivity, wire polylines) are
# MIT. Material derived from CGHD-1152 remains CC BY 4.0: the overlay images
# under ground_truth/net_gt_ui_overlays/, the component annotations under
# ground_truth/component_labels/, and the bboxes in net_gt_ui_meta.json.
# See LICENSE.txt and ground_truth/LICENSE.
license:
  - MIT
  - CC-BY-4.0
keywords:
  - circuit digitization
  - connectivity benchmark
  - graph-based connectivity
  - hand-drawn circuits
  - image-to-netlist
  - netlist extraction
  - schematic recognition
  - SPICE
  - wire extraction
  - wire joining
