    volume, pages, and DOI on acceptance.

# Works this repository builds on. CGHD-1152 is the source of every real
# image used in the benchmark; the overlay images we redistribute are
# adaptations of it and remain under its CC BY 4.0 licence.
references:
  - type: data
    title: 'CGHD1152: A Public Ground-Truth Dataset for Handwritten Circuit Diagram Images'
    authors:
      - given-names: Felix
        family-names: Thoma
      - given-names: Johannes
        family-names: Bayer
      - given-names: Yakun
        family-names: Li
    doi: 10.5281/zenodo.6385814
    url: 'https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6385814'
    license: CC-BY-4.0
    notes: >-
      Source dataset. The overlay images in ground_truth/net_gt_ui_overlays/
      are adaptations of images from this dataset (grayscale conversion,
      bicubic upscaling, and ground-truth wire polylines drawn on top).
